      STR_IMP_TANK_CHASSIS: Alloy Tank Chassis
      STR_IMP_TANK_CHASSIS_UFOPEDIA: Alloy Tank Chassis PlaceHolder
      STR_TANK_LASER_CANNON: Tank/Laser Cannon
      STR_TANK_LASER_CANNON_UFOPEDIA: This small unmanned combat vehicle was designed from the ground up by X-Com team. This remote controlled combat vehicle is clad in alien technology super-alloy armor, equiped with a anti-grav hover module and armed with a laser cannon and improved technology self-loading grenade launcher with 32 HE grenades.
      # ---
      STR_TANK_LASER_GMG: Tank/Laser GMG
      STR_TANK_LASER_GMG_UFOPEDIA: This small unmanned combat vehicle was designed from the ground up by X-Com team. This remote controlled combat vehicle is clad in alien alien technology super-alloy armor, equiped with a anti-grav hover module and armed with a laser technology general machine gun and improved technology self-loading grenade launcher with 32 HE grenades.
      # ---
      STR_TANK_IHROCKET: Tank/Heavy Improved Rocket
      STR_HWP_IHROCKET: HWP Heavy Improved Rocket x8
      STR_TANK_IHROCKET_UFOPEDIA: This small unmanned combat vehicle was designed from the ground up by X-Com team. This remote controlled combat vehicle is clad in alien alien technology super-alloy armor, equiped with a anti-grav hover module and armed with an improved heavy rocket launcher with 8 rockets and laser submachine gun coaxial gun.
      # ---
      STR_TANK_ILROCKET: Tank/Light Improved Rocket
      STR_HWP_ILROCKET: HWP Light Improved Rocket x16
      STR_TANK_ILROCKET_UFOPEDIA: This small unmanned combat vehicle was designed from the ground up by X-Com team. This remote controlled combat vehicle is clad in alien alien technology super-alloy armor, equiped with a anti-grav hover module and armed with an improved light rocket launcher with 16 rockets and laser light machine gun coaxial gun.
      # ---
      AUX_TANK_IGLAUNCHER: HWP 40mm Improved Grenade
      AUX_HWP_IGLAUNCHER: HWP 40mm Improved Grenade x32
      # ---
      AUX_TANK_LASER_LMG: HWP Laser LMG
      # ---      
      AUX_TANK_LASER_SMG: HWP Laser SMG
      # ---
      #STR_HWP_IHROCKET_UFOPEDIA: Using alloy manufacturing techniques to produced high-power nitrocubane explosives, this enhanced heavy HE explosive is the same used in the shoulder launched rocket launcher, just adapted for the auto-loading rocket launcher used by the heavy weapons platform.
      #STR_HWP_ILROCKET_UFOPEDIA: Using the high-power nitrocubane explosives and a super alloy penetrator this enhanced light HE explosive is the same used for the shoulder launched rocket launcher's light rocket and the ISSRL, just adapted for the auto-loading rocket launcher used by the heavy weapons platform.
      #AUX_HWP_IGLAUNCHER_UFOPEDIA: The 40mm HE shell used in the self-loading turret weapon in X-com's heavy weapons platform is improved in every way over the conventional technology both more potent wounding capability, and an increased explosive radius.
      
